+// firstLineHeadIndent (RCTAttributedTextUtils) only covers a paragraph's first line; this covers the
+// remaining case the user hit: a span that soft-wraps to the start of a later line. We only act on
+// soft-wrapped line starts (index 0 and post-newline paragraph starts are left to firstLineHeadIndent
+// so the two mechanisms never double-indent the same line).
+- (BOOL)layoutManager:(NSLayoutManager *)layoutManager
